N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 9500.6 - Sources of funds available for interest

State Regulations

The sources of funds available for the payment of interest
penalties shall be: (a) for the trust
-- the general fund; and
(b) for

Artpark programs -- Artpark revenues, including monies derived from general
appropriations. Notes
